column3: “Well first off it does smell pretty pungent and the smoke is nice and thick it's a heavy I for the head but it's a very Speedy High the exhale is very Woody spicy peppery in the end does taste like diesel fumes like very dirty diesel fumes it's good stuff but I didn't care for The Taste too much I reminded me too much of the strain jet fuel which is another great strain I just don't like the taste very much because e...”
